name: Angular1.X Typescript Systemjs Seed
tagline: Seed project for angular 1.5 with Typescript and systemJS as module loader
body:
### Welcome to my Angular1 typescript SystemJS seed project
Seed project of an application that uses: TypeScript with AngularJS 1.* and SystemJS module loader

includes examples for filters, services, routing,..
for those of you that still cannot migrate to Angular2, this is your best seed friend

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with the project? submit an issue or a pull request
